snippet.title: Diablo 4 - Season of Blood Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description: We're in the middle of Diablo IV Season 1, but check out the trailer for Season 2 Season of Blood, promising even more intense combat as you battle vampiric hordes. Diablo IV Season 2 will be launching October 17
